Decision 94/278/EC is amended as follows:
(a) Part VIII of the Annex is replaced by the text in Annex I to this Decision;
(b) Part XI of the Annex is replaced by the text in Annex II to this Decision;
(c) Part XII of the Annex is replaced by the text in Annex III to this Decision;
(d) Part XIV of the Annex is replaced by the text in Annex IV to this Decision.
